00:00:24,860 --> 00:00:25,060
Sure.

10
00:00:25,420 --> 00:00:27,380
You read the first sentence and it makes perfect sense.

11
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:28,540
You move to the second sentence.

12
00:00:28,540 --> 00:00:30,700
The syntax is, you know, it's holding together.

13
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:32,440
