00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:03,280
It's wildly complex.

148
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:03,700
Yeah.

149
00:07:03,700 --> 00:07:07,420
The clarity arises because the complexity is meticulously scaffolded.

150
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:07,640
Yeah.

151
00:07:07,780 --> 00:07:09,980
Every single logical leap is visible.

152
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:12,580
Every inference is rendered explicit on the page.

153
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:13,560
You can see the work.

154
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:14,160
Yes.

155
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:20,060
If Proposition A is used to derive Proposition B, the structural bridge connecting them is

