908
00:54:28,920 --> 00:54:30,820
Whether that intention exonerates the process

909
00:54:30,820 --> 00:54:32,700
or merely makes it more premeditated

910
00:54:32,700 --> 00:54:35,100
is a question we decline to answer definitively.

911
00:54:35,440 --> 00:54:36,940
It is a masterpiece of trolling.

912
00:54:37,260 --> 00:54:38,920
But it forces the question,

913
00:54:39,480 --> 00:54:41,560
what is the ultimate pedagogical purpose

914
00:54:41,560 --> 00:54:42,440
of this sabotage?

915
00:54:42,440 --> 00:54:44,600
Why ruin a perfectly good paper?

916
00:54:44,600 --> 00:54:46,300
Because it is the only way

917
00:54:46,300 --> 00:54:48,560
to empirically prove their deepest thesis.

918
00:54:49,360 --> 00:54:51,580
That readability is fundamentally contextual,

919
00:54:52,160 --> 00:54:53,720
relational, and experiential.

920
00:54:54,100 --> 00:54:55,980
By actively weaponizing the architecture

921
00:54:55,980 --> 00:54:57,300
of the text against you,

922
00:54:57,820 --> 00:54:59,400
Flyxion forces you to undergo

923
00:54:59,400 --> 00:55:01,720
the exact cognitive rendering failure

924
00:55:01,720 --> 00:55:02,600
they have been describing.

925
00:55:02,780 --> 00:55:03,780
You have to feel it.

926
00:55:03,780 --> 00:55:05,780
Yes, you cannot simply remain

927
00:55:05,780 --> 00:55:06,820
a detached observer,

928
00:55:07,480 --> 00:55:09,120
reading passively about the theory

929
00:55:09,120 --> 00:55:11,300
of the Swedenborg incoherence response.

930
00:55:11,820 --> 00:55:13,180
You are forced to feel it happening

931
00:55:13,180 --> 00:55:14,440
to your own neurology

932
00:55:14,440 --> 00:55:16,180
as your brain struggles to parse

933
00:55:16,180 --> 00:55:17,620
the contravariant functor.

934
00:55:18,000 --> 00:55:19,800
It perfectly bridges the chasm

935
00:55:19,800 --> 00:55:22,080
between abstract linguistic theory

936
00:55:22,080 --> 00:55:23,820
and visceral phenomenology.

937
00:55:23,820 --> 00:55:25,900
It is an elite-level magic trick.

938
00:55:26,120 --> 00:55:27,600
They pull the rug out from underneath you,

939
00:55:27,680 --> 00:55:28,740
but as you are falling,

940
00:55:28,900 --> 00:55:30,640
they hand you a perfectly drafted blueprint

941
00:55:30,640 --> 00:55:32,320
of the rug and the floor mechanics.

942
00:55:32,320 --> 00:55:33,660
But just when you believe

943
00:55:33,660 --> 00:55:35,480
the riot has come to a complete stop,

944
00:55:35,800 --> 00:55:37,520
just as Flyxion mercifully switches

945
00:55:37,520 --> 00:55:38,900
